snippet.title: Texting of the Bread - Wave 48 (Opie & Anthony)
snippet.description: All the levels in Texting of the Bread have themes for their words.  Being a fan of Opie & Anthony as well as one of the level designers for the game, I decided to make Wave 48 a sort of O&A appreciation level. http://TrepidStudios.com/
